enb_long_title: Thirteenth Session of the Subsidiary Bodies of the UNFCCC
sentences: SBSTA also addressed Protocol Articles 5 (methodological issues), 7 (communication of information) and 8 (review of information).
Group Co-Chair Helen Plume (New Zealand) noted that substantial work remained.
A contact group was established to continue discussions.
On cooperation with relevant international organizations, the Secretariat noted recent cooperative work with the Convention on Biodiversity.
